Enchantments.description: A list of enchantments that are on the item

HideFlags.description:
Bitfield for which flags to hide on an item  
 1 -> `Enchantments`  
 2 -> `AttributeModifiers`  
 4 -> `Unbreakable`  
 8 -> `CanDestroy`  
 16 -> `CanPlaceOn` (for block items)  
 32 -> other misc info

CanDestroy.description: A list of the block states that can be destroyed by this item when holding it in adventure mode

Damage.description: The damage that an item has. Only used for tools, armor, etc

CustomModelData.description:
A tag that describes the custom model an item will take.  
 Gets used by the `custom_model_data` model predicate

compound_arena.description: An individual enchantment, with ID and level

Slot.description: The slot that the modifier is active in

Name.description: Name of the modifier, has no real effect

compound_arena.description: The display settings of an item

Name.description: The name of an item, as a JSON text component

Lore.description: The lore of an item, with each element being a lore line

compound_arena.description: An item that has a potion effect

CustomPotionEffects.description: A list of the potion effects that will be used with this item

Potion.description: The name of the default potion effect

CustomPotionColor.description:
Color of this item  
 calculated as `RED << 16 | GREEN << 8 | BLUE`. Each of these fields must be between 0 and 255, inclusive

compound_arena.description: An item that can spawn an entity

EntityTag.description: The data of the spawned entity

pages.description: The pages of the book as JSON text components

resolved.description: Whether the dynamic content on the pages has been resolved

Effects.description: The effects this stew will give

EffectDuration.description: The duration of the effect in ticks

Name.description: Name of the owner, if missing appears as a steve head

Value.description: Base64 encoded JSON value of the texture

BucketVariantTag.description: The variant of fish. Only used for tropical fish

Flight.description: Flight duration of the firework rocket

FadeColors.description:
The colors of the explosion fade  
 calculated as `RED << 16 | GREEN << 8 | BLUE`. Each of these fields must be between 0 and 255, inclusive

Trail.description: Whether the explosion should have a trail

Colors.description:
The colors of the explosion  
 calculated as `RED << 16 | GREEN << 8 | BLUE`. Each of these fields must be between 0 and 255, inclusive

Base.description: The base color of the shield

compound_arena.description: An item that can be placed as a block

BlockStateTag.description: The block states that the placed block will have

BlockEntityTag.description: The tags that the block entity that is placed can have

CanPlaceOn.description: A list of block states that this block item can be placed on

map_scale_direction.description: The amount to increase the current map scale by when crafting

x.description: The world x position of the decoration

id.description: An arbitrary string identifying the decoration

rot.description: The rotation of the decoration, measured in degrees clockwise

z.description: The world z position of the decoration

MapColor.description:

ChargedProjectiles.description: The projectiles loaded into the crossbow

Recipes.description: The recipes this book can give

color.description:
The color of the armor

compound_arena.description:
A compass.
 May either point to a specific coordinate or the world spawn

LodestoneDimension.description: The dimension the lodestone is in

LodestoneTracked.description:
Whether the compass should be linked to a lodestone.
 When true, the compass will reset if the lodestone at the position is removed.

Count.description: The number of items in the stack

Slot.description: The inventory slot the item is in

Ambient.description: Whether the effect particles are semi-transparent (like with a Beacon)

ShowParticles.description: Whether the effect particles should be shown

ShowIcon.description: Whether the effect icon should be shown

RightOfDiagonal.description: Right of Diagonal (Per bend sinister inverted)

LeftOfUpsideDownDiagonal.description: Left of upside-down Diagonal (Per bend inverted)

Percentage.description:
For every modifier, multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the amount of the particular modifier.
 Functions the same as Operation 1 if there is only a single modifier with operation 1 or 2.
 However, for multiple modifiers it will multiply the modifiers rather than adding them

Additive.description: Adds all of the modifiers' amounts to the current value of the attribute

Multiplicative.description:
Multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the sum of the modifiers' amounts.
